external_knowledge:
- The average number of grants is calculated across all categories and programs;
- The query focuses on categories and programs that exceed this average;
- The results are sorted by the total grant amount to highlight the most significant programs.

- 'Total amount of water they have received' refers to the sum of the `amount_disbursed` for each grant;
- 'Most nourished' refers to the grants with the highest total disbursements;
- 'Purposes' refer to the `description` of the grants;
- 'Programs they belong to' refer to the `program_name` of the programs;
- 'Categories they fall under' refer to the `category_name` of the categories.
